---
---

<section class="hero is-in" id="top">
  <div class="wrap hero__grid">
    <div class="hero__copy">
      <span class="label" data-reveal>Realtime voice judge</span>

      <h1 class="display hero__title" data-reveal data-delay="1">
        The judge that<br />
        interrupts <span class="serif-italic accent">before</span><br />
        the real judges do.
      </h1>

      <p class="hero__lede" data-reveal data-delay="2">
        You pitch out loud. PitchPilot listens, and the second it hears a soft
        spot — no clear problem, a thin “why you”, no demo, no benchmark, too
        much jargon — it cuts in. Say <span class="mono">“score me”</span> and it
        hands back a scorecard.
      </p>

      <div class="hero__cta" data-reveal data-delay="3">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#how">See how it works</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#scorecard">Read a scorecard →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- live session mock -->
    <div class="session" data-reveal data-delay="2" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="session__bar">
        <span class="dot"></span>
        <span class="session__room mono">room · judgemode</span>
        <span class="session__live">LIVE</span>
      </div>

      <div class="session__body">
        <p class="line line--you"><span class="who mono">you</span>So, um, our app is like an AI platform that leverages synergies to…</p>
        <p class="line line--you line--fade"><span class="who mono">you</span>…disrupt the, the productivity space for everyone, basically—</p>

        <div class="cut">
          <span class="cut__tag">JUDGE CUTS IN</span>
          <p class="cut__text">Stop. <em>Who</em> exactly has this problem, and what do they do today instead?</p>
        </div>

        <div class="wave">
          <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
          <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
          <span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding-block: clamp(3rem, 8vh, 6.5rem) clamp(4rem, 9vh, 7rem);
  }
  .hero__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    align-items: center;
  }
  .hero__title {
    font-size: clamp(2.7rem, 6.6vw, 5rem);
    margin-block: 1.1rem 1.6rem;
    color: var(--navy);
  }
  .accent { color: var(--orange); }
  .hero__lede {
    font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 1.5vw, 1.22rem);
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 34ch;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .hero__lede .mono { color: var(--navy); font-weight: 500; }
  .hero__cta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.9rem;
    margin-top: 2.1rem;
  }

  /* ---- session panel ---- */
  .session {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--navy);
    border-radius: 4px;
    box-shadow: 10px 12px 0 rgba(40, 52, 122, 0.1);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .session__bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    padding: 0.7rem 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    background: var(--paper-2);
  }
  .dot {
    width: 9px;
    height: 9px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--orange);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(255, 93, 48, 0.5);
    animation: pulse 1.8s infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pulse {
    0% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(255, 93, 48, 0.5); }
    70% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 7px rgba(255, 93, 48, 0); }
    100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(255, 93, 48, 0); }
  }
  .session__room { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); }
  .session__live {
    margin-left: auto;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.66rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--orange);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .session__body { padding: 1.3rem 1.3rem 1.5rem; }

  .line {
    font-size: 0.96rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--navy-ink);
    margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 3.2rem;
  }
  .who {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.1rem;
    font-size: 0.66rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }
  .line--fade { opacity: 0.55; }

  .cut {
    margin: 1rem 0 0.4rem;
    padding: 0.9rem 1rem 1rem;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--orange);
    background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--orange) 9%, #fff);
    border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
    animation: cutin 600ms cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1) 700ms both;
  }
  @keyframes cutin {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-10px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
  }
  .cut__tag {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--orange-deep);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .cut__text {
    margin-top: 0.4rem;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.12rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--navy);
  }
  .cut__text em { color: var(--orange-deep); font-style: italic; }

  .wave {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    gap: 4px;
    height: 30px;
    margin-top: 1.1rem;
  }
  .wave span {
    flex: 1;
    background: var(--navy-soft);
    border-radius: 2px;
    height: 30%;
    animation: bar 1s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .wave span:nth-child(odd) { background: var(--navy); }
  .wave span:nth-child(3n) { animation-delay: 0.15s; }
  .wave span:nth-child(3n+1) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  .wave span:nth-child(4n) { animation-delay: 0.45s; }
  @keyframes bar {
    0%, 100% { height: 22%; }
    50% { height: 90%; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .session { order: 2; max-width: 480px; }
  }
</style>
